name: Baby Bali
description: We are the first token to combine these 4 super elements at once. We chose the tourism sector as a priority in this project, especially Bali tourism. We believe that with our innovations, we can contribute to revitalising Bali's tourism sector after the pandemic. We're also very sure, that with the vaccination program being intensively carried out in Indonesia, the heyday of Bali tourism will soon be repeated. When that happens, then Baby Bali products will be perfectly in the right time, and in the right place.
